content: I love this app it has help me so much
Great app, but please add the ability to view videos offline. Very frustrating when traveling or in the field and I'm unable to use.

RTTs for 249 and 240 are outdated on here. Please update and it will be very useful. The main difference is you hold the charging handle back while you place it on safety, then return it forward. A big enough difference for the videos to be updated especially since its an app we have to pay for. Other than that great app
replyContent: Thank you for the review Eric. We are currently updating the RTTs. Good Luck in Ranger School!

content: A great resource to have on hand. When can we expect an update for the RTT standards? Edit: Thank you for your quick response! I appreciate the assistance!
replyContent: Thank you for taking the time to leave a review. As things often change with any course we are trying to make new videos with the new changes. The current content will get you 90% or more and once you arrive at RS you will be given time to practice. Good luck and one day at a time. UTD

content: Good app however the following are potential problems I found.. Following need be possibly updated Packing list from 2018. Class dates are 2019. The following PDFs are not opening. Boot policy, ARTB comanders letter, artb cms letter, building mental toughness for ranger school, ranger school preparation, sample ranger school training... I look forward to veiwing the rest of the app and leaving my input. Everything ranger school all in one place and wall organized.
Very easy to use. Has a lot of detailed videos.

RTT's are not taught correctly. Does not properly clear the 249 before firing becaise clearing of the top cover does not have a top to bottom sweep and does not make the right to left sweep of the feed tray deliberate. After firing the 249, fails to put the safery on fire with the charging handle to the rear. would not be a go at ranger school. Does not provide the standards for the event unless you pay am extra $10.

Excellent app that has all of the tactical information an Infantryman could want for small unit tactics. A one stop source for any aspiring Infantryman who wants to be prepared for the U.S. Army Ranger School. Easy to use and to navigate, with doctrinal knowledge at your fingertip!
Awesome app. Extremely easy to nagivate. the app has a ton of information that will prepare any Soldier for Ranger school.
New app is easy to navigate. Best app to prepare you for Ranger School, you will not find anything better.

This is one of the best school/training apps that I have used. Not only will the information on this app set you up for success when you go to Ranger School but it will also help you train your Soldiers. The fact that it is straight forward and easy to use makes it that much better. I recommend this app to all my Junior Leaders and Soldiers.
great update to an amazing App, every Combat Arms Soldier needs to have this App
alot of valuable info

Great app. Use it during some down time, while deployed. Gives any individual a little head start before hitting the school. I would give this app 5 stars however, I've been waiting for the app to be complete. STILL MISSING FLORIDA PLEASE UPDATE!!!! other then that little bit, please keep up the great work. Some of use need any advantage we can get.
Sensational
This app does nothing. Ranger school is all luck. No preparing for it.

More interesting than the ranger handbook. App has nice design, good content, all your necessary FM. I love the work! Ready for Florida phase to be completed, it's good to have an advantage in the phase most recycled.  "Know before you go"
More video's
Great way to learn, before they try teaching you this when you are hungry and tired
Great app but I used to be able to access a ranger school preparation workout routine, I can't find it now. Was it removed? If not, please tell me where I can find it again

Upper Tier Development, when is the Florida phase coming out?  That's the last piece of the puzzle to this already amazing app.  I just finished SOF CCC and the OPORD portion was a good refresher to my ranger school days. Thanks for the work you put into this.
Sucks. There's nothing in here that will help you. All it does is tell you what happens absolutely do not suggest paying for this.
replyContent: So all the tips under lessons learned from over 3 years of Ranger graduates and recycles is nothing? Or all the videos that goes over operations order, TLP, and squad level tactics? But not to mention we show you all the Ranger Tactical Tasks and knots so you can get a Major Plus... ha we laugh at you trolls. I don't know why you waste your time...

content: This app is great. Everything is consolidated nicely. If videos are slow just change the quality.
Best app ever!
Can't wait to explore and learn new techniques and shake off the dust of what is already known, looking forward to the knots.

This app is definitely a game changer as you can familiarize yourself with the knowledge before you actually attend.  It's got boards, videos, and narratives to accomdate for different learning styles. It'll cover things such as general info about Ranger school, tips, Ranger tactical tasks, knots, and patrolling. Hope they can finish the Florida phase soon with the next update. Overall, I can't see how future Ranger school students can attend without checking this app out.
gives great information and functions well but is missing pertinent information for Florida phase
The app is ok but the videos don't load properly and when they do they constantly pause. When you attempt to replay it or even navigate through the app the delay is frustrating.
replyContent: Change the resolution to 360. If you don't have fast enough internet the videos will take time to buffer.

content: A great one stop shop for all your Ranger School questions in a format that is easy to navigate and constantly updated. What's that you say? "I've already been to school" say no more, this app also serves as a great refresher for those who already went. Want to give a class to your guys but because you were a Solar Powered Ranger you forgot some stuff. So instead of digging through some boring FM,TC, or the book of books (SH 21-76) you can fire this bad boy up and get it from the professionals.
Very helpful staff
Love it thanks
This app doesn't tell anyone anything they can't find out from the school before going. What I want to see is how to pass patrols. which has been saying coming soon for two months now
replyContent: If you're not smart enough to use the app to increase your chances on passing your patrols or Ranger School then you may want to consider holding off going. To everybody else there is no secret handshake to passing Ranger School. This app has the classes from Ranger School so you don't have to learn them there while you're fighting to stay awake!

content: Highly recommend this app to anyone planning on attending Ranger School or even Infantry and Combat Arms team leaders and squad leaders who want to enhance their knowledge base. Looking forward to versions 2.0 and 3.0!

Ranger prep made easy! You still gotta do the hard work, but this app has all the goods in one place. I used similar information to prepare myself for Ranger School but I had to hunt around and collect it myself. If you dedicate yourself to learning what's in this app so that you can preform when it's game time...you will definitely set yourself up for success.

Very well done. Lots of great information, especially the instructional videos. It's a must have if you're getting ready for Ranger School. This is a great resource to have if your on the line. Looking forward to the Mountain and Florida phase updates.
This app is everything it says it is. Highly recommended for those needing a refresher or about to go Ranger.
Would recommend for anyone wanting to be successful at Ranger school
This app is a great tool for someone who wants to prepare for Ranger School, have a quick reference for hip-pocket training, or maintain their base of knowledge in individual and unit tasks.

This is a great tool for any Combat Arms Soldier.  The training materials contained in this app cover most of the basic and advanced critical tasks needed to operate successfully in the field environment .  If you are preparing for Ranger School, having the most up to date information (along with example videos) concerning Ranger tasks and the ability to interact with current RIs is worth the price of admission.  Highly recommended.
I would recommend this app to anyone wanting to be successful through Ranger school.

I wish this app was available a 6 months. It tell you everything you need to know to be successful and proficient in the skills required to pass ranger school. If you have the heart, this app will give you the skill set needed to get the tab. I am going to be recommended this to everyone in my unit that wishes to go to Ranger School. Great app!!!
Very helpful and great layout! Love it!
